Deepin Installer

用法：
  deepin-installer [选项...] - Deepin Installer

帮助选项：
  -h, --help                       显示帮助选项
  --help-all                       显示全部帮助选项
  --help-gtk                       显示 GTK+ 选项

应用程序选项：
  -s, --schema=fast or safe        fast use unsquashfs, safe copy file one by one
  -c, --cpu=count                  num of processors used in unsquashfs mode
  -i, --iso=path                   set iso file path when install without live os
  -a, --automatic                  gather info from command line then install automatic
  -t, --target=/dev/sdaX           device to install system, required when automatic
  -m, --home=/dev/sdaX             partition mount as home in target system, only work when automatic
  -u, --username=deepin            username of target system, required when automatic
  -n, --hostname=hostname          hostname of target system, only work when automatic
  -p, --password=password          password of target system, required when automatic
  -l, --layout=layout code         keyboard layout of target system, only work when automatic
  -v, --variant=variant code       keyboard variant of target system, only work when automatic
  -z, --zone=Asia/Shanghai         timezone of target system, only work when automatic
  -e, --locale=zh_CN.UTF-8         locale of target system, only work when automatic
  -g, --grub=/dev/sdaX or uefi     device path or uefi to install bootloader, only work when automatic
  -d, --debug                      set log level to debug
  --display=显示                   要使用的 X 显示
